TrueDepth Front-facing Camera Usage
Inner Garden uses TrueDepth front-facing camera on supported iOS devices to track the position of user's face and expressions, eg. eye movement, mouth openness. Inner Garden then uses these information to determine user‚Äôs focus of attention and calculate user‚Äôs focus level. The camera data is used and disposed in real-time anonymously for app to function only. It will NOT be stored on device or distributed to any third parties.
Non-TrueDepth Front-facing Camera Usage
Inner Garden uses front-facing camera on iOS devices to recognize and track the position of user's face. Inner Garden then uses these information to calculate user‚Äôs attention level. The camera data is used and disposed in real-time anonymously for app to function only. It will NOT be stored on device or distributed to any third parties.
Microphone Usage
Inner Garden uses built-in microphone on iOS devices to detect ambient sound volume. Inner Garden then uses these information to calculate user‚Äôs attention level. The microphone data will NOT be recorded, stored, or distributed to any third parties.
Freeland uses built-in microphone on iOS devices to detect ambient sound volume. Freeland then uses these information to simulate the action of blowing away objects like flowers and foliages. The microphone data will NOT be recorded, stored, or distributed to any third parties.
